sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (SDK/UI)
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>9000/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Driver as Driver (sidecar)<br/>Go CLI
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher (sidecar)<br/>Go CLI
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SWCtrl as Scheduled Workflow Controller
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,Launcher: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>HTTP 8888 | Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>SQL 3306/5432 | Username/Password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline spec<br/>HTTP 9000 | AccessKey/SecretKey
    API->>K8s: Submit Argo Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443 | SA Token
    K8s-->>Argo: Watch event: new Workflow
    Argo->>Driver: Execute driver step<br/>Pod exec
    Driver->>MLMD: Record execution context<br/>gRPC 8080 | Optional TLS
    Driver->>API: Cache lookup (TaskService)<br/>gRPC 8887 | Optional TLS
    API-->>Driver: Cache miss/hit response
    Argo->>Launcher: Execute user container<br/>Pod exec
    Launcher->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000 | AccessKey/SecretKey
    Note over Launcher: Execute user code
    Launcher->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000 | AccessKey/SecretKey
    Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution results<br/>gRPC 8080 | Optional TLS

    Note over User,PA: Flow 2: Recurring Run Scheduling

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>HTTP 8888 | Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443 | SA Token
    K8s-->>SWCtrl: Watch event: new ScheduledWorkflow
    SWCtrl->>API: CreateRun (on schedule)<br/>gRPC 8887 | Projected SA Token

    Note over PA,API: Flow 3: Workflow Status Persistence

    PA->>K8s: Watch Argo Workflows<br/>HTTPS 443 | SA Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status update
    PA->>API: ReportWorkflow<br/>gRPC 8887 | Projected SA Token

    Note over K8s,Cache: Flow 4: Pipeline Step Caching (v1 Webhook)

    K8s->>Cache: Pod admission request<br/>HTTPS 443 | K8s client cert
    Cache->>DB: Check cache (cachedb)<br/>SQL 3306 | Username/Password
    Cache-->>K8s: AdmissionResponse<br/>(mutate pod if cache hit)
